        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare mitochondrial oxidative phosphorylation disorder due to large-scale single deletion of mitochondrial DNA characterized by hyporegenerative anemia in early infancy with vacuolization of bone marrow precursors lactic acidosis and multi-organ dysfunctions such as exocrine pancreatic dysfunction and renal tubulopathy."
        },
